  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1077430/extras/c2a6413dbd6ba7b152104eaab48f0b6c.avif?t=1589974427\" width=623 height=228 /></span><br><br><strong>There's a Butcher Around, a brutal hide & seek. Bill the butcher has escaped from the asylum and is looking for new victims.<br><br>During the game you will have to find a place to hide, remembering that your friends are also trying to hide from the butcher. Every round, Bill the butcher chooses a spot to investigate, are you well hidden?<br><br>The main goal is to be the last survivor, so find the best place to hide.<br>Game contains a climate of terror, suspense and lots of blood, plus some references of our taste.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>17 playable characters<br></li><li>7 maps<br></li><li>Tense atmosphere<br></li><li>Fun gameplay<br></li><li>Pixel art<br></li><li>Full Compatibility with Control<br></li><li>Steam Achievements</li></ul></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1077430/extras/1f6e2c6b4e630269a9cc9419d5a42922.webp?t=1589974427\" width=623 height=52 /></span>",
